{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a6718bf630","title":"给叶剑英的信","origin":"根据网络材料打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7f643ef3c5","index":0,"year":1974,"month":6,"day":1,"articleId":"a6718bf630"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0561be065a","name":"白智清"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d5cf23fd54","type":"title","text":"给叶剑英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"d64bbc794c","type":"authors","text":"白智清","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"38ed67f8aa","type":"appellation","text":"敬爱的叶帅：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"10591a0291","type":"paragraph","text":"我们深深知道，您非常爱国家，非常爱人民，难道你未看见在那群恶狗的践踏下，中国落到了国亡无日的田地?他们把矛头对准总理和所有的老干部，稍有一点爱国心的人，有哪一个不想吃这群恶狗的肉，喝这群恶狗的血啊！军内军外，党内党外，上上下下，人们的眼睛都快要冒火了。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"efc618fa5d","type":"paragraph","text":"叶帅，敬爱的叶帅，为了拯救国家，拯救民族，因势利导，担负起这个沉重又伟大的担子吧，我想第一步，告诉军队，没有总理、你、小平的名字，不管谁都调不动！！！我们相信军队是听你们话的。第二步，对林彪系统的将士，只能安抚，不能压服，以免搞出问题，不要逼上梁山。我想他们其中绝大多数人都是恨这群狗和爱国的，还是听你们的话的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"c8d4d6c812","type":"paragraph","text":"叶帅，农夫惜蛇被蛇咬，放虎归山虎伤人。是干的时候了。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"1c1d9726fa","type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国的富强","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"42bc2228d0","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"},{"id":"0ff8d23db0","type":"paragraph","text":" 心赤客敬上一九七四年六月一日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630"}],"page":{"id":"da2c2be63c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a6718bf630","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}